{"tid":517601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐警者庭外見陳展鵬 高叫「支持朱經緯」","createTime":"2018-01-02T12:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T12:52:39.000Z","uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7fd129ec83c845509957cc85a08a6cea9b1cbc","tid":517601,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20171111/s00007/86d573b5bb0f07ad31d6a7f04884bf2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20171111%2Fs00007%2F86d573b5bb0f07ad31d6a7f04884bf2d.jpg&h=cb181959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】藝人陳展鵬被票控不小心駕駛罪，案件昨於東區裁判法院提堂，陳展鵬到庭應訊，否認控罪。他離開法院時駐足讓記者拍照，由於警司朱經緯涉襲擊途人案亦於同一裁判法院審理，守在法院外的朱經緯支持者此時高呼「支持朱經緯」近1分鐘，未知是否認錯人。"},{"pid":"4a8bd6d3093157cda8d06792fa1a5dbcccfbb533","tid":517601,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"啱啱放監?"},{"pid":"fcfb0ef04f03b7b144c53fb272ff65d092ce7420","tid":517601,"uid":164928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"屌 2017D料都番炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}